data.description: Beautiful home in the tall pines! Situated on .46 acres, this 2 bed 2 bath home offers serene views of the ponderosa forest while being conveniently located only 10 minutes from Prescott's historic downtown. Cozy up to the wood burning stove while enjoying the fabulous views from the vaulted living room windows. The attached oversized two car garage boasts lots of storage space and plenty of room for your cars or toys. The primary bedroom features its own generously sized ensuite bathroom, with another full-sized bathroom on the main level. If you're looking to enjoy a piece of tranquility in the pines, come check out this haven today!
